---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Web Applications | Jay Software - Fast, Scalable, Revenue-Boosting"
  description="Stop losing customers to slow websites. Custom web applications that load in under 2 seconds, increase conversions by 40-80%, and scale to millions of users. Free performance audit."
  keywords="web application development, custom web apps, scalable web solutions, responsive web development, enterprise web applications, SaaS development, progressive web apps"
  canonicalUrl="https://jay-software.com/services/web-applications"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900/20 to-blue-900/20 border-b border-slate-700">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600/20 border border-green-500/30 rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-green-300 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
            🌐 Web Applications
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Stop Losing Customers to
            <span class="text-red-400">Slow</span>, Outdated Websites
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Modern web applications that load in under 2 seconds, convert 40-80% better, and scale to millions of users. Built with cutting-edge technology.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/#strategic-consultation" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-600 hover:from-green-700 hover:to-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
              Get Web App Performance Audit
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problems Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Is Your Website <span class="text-red-400">Bleeding Revenue</span>?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            Every second of load time costs you 7% of conversions. Here's what's hurting your business...
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🐌</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Glacial Load Times</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Pages taking 5+ seconds to load, causing 50%+ visitor abandonment before they see your content.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">📱</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Mobile Disasters</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Websites that look broken on phones, losing 60% of your potential customers.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🔒</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Security Vulnerabilities</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Outdated platforms vulnerable to attacks, risking customer data and your reputation.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">📉</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Poor SEO Rankings</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Invisible to Google, losing thousands of potential customers to competitors.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">💸</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Low Conversion Rates</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Poor user experience turning visitors into lost revenue instead of customers.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🛠️</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Maintenance Nightmares</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Constant bugs, crashes, and expensive maintenance eating into profits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
              Web Applications That <span class="text-green-400">Convert & Scale</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Lightning-fast, mobile-first applications built with modern technology that grows your business.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Sub-2 Second Load Times</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Optimized for speed with modern frameworks and CDN delivery.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-blue-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Mobile-First Design</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Perfect experience on every device, from phones to desktops.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-purple-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Enterprise Security</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Bank-level security with SSL, encryption, and regular security audits.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-amber-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">40-80% Higher Conversions</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Optimized user experience designed to turn visitors into customers.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What You Get:</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Modern React/Next.js or Vue.js architecture</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Progressive Web App capabilities</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">SEO optimization & Google Analytics</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Cloud hosting & automatic backups</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">24/7 monitoring & maintenance</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Technologies Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Built With <span class="text-blue-400">Cutting-Edge Technology</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            We use the latest frameworks and tools for maximum performance and scalability
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-blue-400 text-3xl mb-4">⚛️</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">React/Next.js</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Modern, fast, and SEO-friendly frontend frameworks</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-green-500/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-green-400 text-3xl mb-4">🟢</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Node.js</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">High-performance server-side JavaScript runtime</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-purple-400 text-3xl mb-4">🗄️</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Cloud Databases</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">PostgreSQL, MongoDB, or Redis for optimal performance</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-amber-400 text-3xl mb-4">☁️</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">AWS/Vercel</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Global CDN and cloud infrastructure for reliability</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Studies -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Web Applications That Drive Results
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            Real performance improvements and revenue growth
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-green-500/20 rounded-xl p-8">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">SaaS Platform</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Complete redesign and performance optimization</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center mb-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">85%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Faster Load Times</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">65%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Higher Conversions</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">$180K</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Extra Annual Revenue</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic">
              "The new web application doubled our signup rate and reduced customer support tickets by 40%."
            </blockquote>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-xl p-8">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">E-commerce Store</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Modern checkout and mobile optimization</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center mb-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">78%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Mobile Conversions</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">45%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Cart Abandonment</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">320%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">ROI Increase</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic">
              "Mobile sales increased 300% after the redesign. The investment paid for itself in 2 months."
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-900/20 to-blue-900/20 border-t border-slate-700">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Ready for a Web Application That <span class="text-green-400">Actually Converts</span>?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Stop losing customers to slow, outdated websites. Get a modern web application that drives results.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/#strategic-consultation" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-600 hover:from-green-700 hover:to-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
              Get Web App Performance Audit
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
              </svg>
              Back to Home
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout> 